==English==
===Etymology===
From [[Indonesian]] ''[[Orang Betawi]]'' "people of [[Batavia]]"

===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Betawi'''

#[[Indonesian]] [[ethnic]] group consisting of the descendants of the people living around [[Batavia]] ([[Jakarta]]) from around the 17th century.

